node.text:
Let’s talk “Getting Unstuck & Getting to the Bag” 
.
Starting my entrepreneurial journey in 2017 I was very stuck. Stuck in my head, stuck in not believing in myself, stuck in not knowing if I made the right decision for full time entrepreneurship over going back to a job I hated and stuck in not knowing my worth that I am worthy of this lifestyle that I never thought was possible. 
.
. 
You know what got me unstuck, helping families get affordable housing. Helping my people secure financial freedom through a sector that was unheard of and knowing the impact I have on these changed lives. But on top of that, being around like-minded women, women who I can laugh hysterically with, kick it with but also hold me accountable to ensure we are all “Getting to the bag” 🤑
.
.
That is why I am coming together with my sisters @rashaunascott @bryana.randolph @wanakeemarie to bring you B.U.I.L.D & brunch where we will be discussing Branding, Unifying, Impacting, Leading & Diversifying amongst women who are ready to go to that next level.
.
.
Are you ready to join us at the 7 figure table? Come sit down with us for an intimate VIP brunch & intensive panel where you will leave inspired, encouraged and feeling no doubts of wanting to knock down every goal you have this year. 
.
.
CLICK THE LINK IN THE BIO NOW TO SECURE YOUR SPOT. Limited tickets available for brunch.  See you there! 
.
.
.
.
.
#mobilehomeeliteinvestors 
#womenempowerment 
#womencominhtogether 
#buildandbrunch 
#chicago

node.text:
Before hiring a handy man for your mobile home renovations, WATCH THIS VIDEO!

Be sure to ask them the following:

✅ What do you specialize in?

✅ How many mobile homes have you renovated?

✅ What is your average turn around time?

✅ Can you walk me through a previous property or do you have pics of your work?

These are a few questions you can ask to assure you are finding the right handy man. 

We’re guessing you haven’t got around to it, but did you know we offer hands on mentoring? Schedule a call with one of our Elite Strategy coaches to learn how you can work directly with us! Click the link in our bio to set up a call to learn about our Elite Fast Track 5 Week Program. 
.
.
.

#mobilehomeinvesting 
#mobilehomehandymen
